            <blockquote class="text-cream/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              "Joe tuned up my commuter bike and it rides like new. Fair prices, honest work, and done the same day. Can't ask for more."
            </blockquote>
            <cite class="text-sm text-cream/40 font-medium not-italic">— Sarah M., Kensington</cite>
          </div>

          <div class="p-7 rounded-2xl bg-cream/5 border border-cream/10">
